feat(kyc): integrate PlayGuard age verification (PredictStreet compliance)

Mandatory biometric age check at registration via AWS Rekognition through
PlayGuard. Minors are auto-blocked, ambiguous cases flagged for manual
review, and every scan is audited in Supabase.

Database (supabase/migrations/2026-05-23-playguard-kyc.sql):
- New table public.kyc_checks (verdict, age_low/high, estimated_age,
  is_minor, confidence, scan_id, FK to users, RLS service-role-only).
- public.users.kyc_status text default 'pending' with CHECK constraint
  (pending|approved|denied|verify_age).
- public.users.blocked boolean default false (also fixes the dangling
  reference in /api/admin/users/:id/block).

Backend (server/routes/kyc.ts, registered in server/index.ts):
- POST /api/kyc/scan { user_id, selfie_b64 } → forwards to the PlayGuard
  Vercel Edge proxy with PG_API_KEY (server-side env, never bundled).
- Maps verdicts:
    APPROVED        → users.kyc_status='approved'
    DENIED / minor  → users.kyc_status='denied' + users.blocked=true
    VERIFY_AGE      → users.kyc_status='verify_age'
- Inserts the audit row into kyc_checks unconditionally (logged on error
  but does not fail the user-facing call).
- 403 if the supplied user_id is already blocked.
- 502 with friendly error if PlayGuard upstream is unreachable.
- New env vars: PG_API_KEY (required), PG_PROXY_URL (defaults to
  https://playguard.vercel.app/api/proxy).

Admin API (server/routes/admin.ts):
- /api/admin/overview now returns kyc { approved, pending, denied,
  verify_age } counts.
- /api/admin/users list exposes kyc_status & blocked per row.
- /api/admin/users/:id includes the last 5 kyc_checks for the audit
  trail.

Frontend:
- src/screens/KycScreen.tsx — 4-stage flow (capture → preview → loading →
  result) using getUserMedia, square-cropped JPEG, mirrored preview.
  APPROVED → /, DENIED → clearSession + /splash, VERIFY_AGE → / with
  manual-review banner.
- src/lib/auth.ts — SessionUser now carries kyc_status + blocked.
  loginUser refuses blocked accounts. New refreshKycStatus() helper.
- src/lib/api.ts — api.kycScan(user_id, selfie_b64).
- src/App.tsx — /kyc route + Protected guard: blocked/denied → splash,
  pending → /kyc, approved/verify_age → through. KycRoute itself bypasses
  the guard to break the redirect loop.
- src/screens/RegisterScreen.tsx & LoginScreen.tsx — route based on
  user.kyc_status post-auth.

Admin UI:
- src/screens/admin/KycBadge.tsx — single source of truth for the pills
  (approved=green, pending=grey, denied=red, verify_age=amber).
- PlayersTab — KYC column in the players table, badge in the drawer
  header, and a new "Vérifications KYC" audit table (last 5).
- OverviewTab — "X vérifiés / Y en attente / Z à vérifier / W refusés"
  KPI block under the existing grid.

Build: npm run build && npm run build:server → 0 errors.

Render env vars to set: PG_API_KEY (required, must match PlayGuard).
